	<article class="post-155974 post type-post status-publish hentry category-disunion tag-blacks tag-civil-war-us-1861-65 tag-international-relations tag-united-states-defense-and-military-forces des-blacks des-civil-war-us-1861-65 des-international-relations des-united-states-defense-and-military-forces news_keywords-american-civil-war news_keywords-blacks news_keywords-international-relations-2 news_keywords-us-military-2" id="post-155974">
	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
			<span class="kicker"><a href="//opinionator.blogs.nytimes.com/category/disunion/?module=BlogCategory&version=Blog Post&action=Click&contentCollection=Opinion&pgtype=Blogs&region=Header">Disunion</a></span>
